# Force consistent line endings and prevent Git from ever transcoding
# this repo's text files. The previous submission lost every emoji and
# em dash because an editor/tool round-tripped the file through a
# non-UTF-8 codepage. These rules keep that from happening again.

* text=auto eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.js   text eol=lf
*.css  text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md   text eol=lf

# Treat these as binary so Git never attempts line-ending/encoding
# normalisation on them.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
